            <div type="transcript" id="F614A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>'Twas warm - at first - like<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Us -</l>
                    <l>Until there crept opon </l>
                    <l>A Chill - like frost opon<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 a Glass - </l>
                    <l>Till all the scene - be gone.  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Forehead copied stone -</l>
                    <l>The Fingers grew too cold </l>
                    <l>To ache - and like a<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Skater's Brook - </l>
                    <l>The busy eyes - congealed - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>It straightened - that was all - </l>
                    <l>It crowded Cold to Cold -</l>
                    <l>It multiplied indifference - </l>
                    <l>As Pride were all it could - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And even when with Cords - </l>
                    <l>'Twas lowered, like a Weight -<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>It made no Signal, nor<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 demurred,</l>
                    <l>But dropped like Adamant.  </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
